Description: # YAML Helper
        
        Helper methods to read and write `.yml` files.
        
        ## Installation
        `pip install yaml-helper`
        
        ## Usage
        ```
        import yaml_helper as yaml
        
        
        yml_file = 'config.yml'
        yml = yaml.load(yml_file)
        additional = {'driver': 'mysqli'}
        
        yaml.add(additional)
        ```
        
